<p>I'm using jwplayer 7 javascript version. It works nice. Just one thing when video starts to play on portrait it should stay on its own area but on landscape it should go to fullscreen.</p>  <p>This code works perfectly on htc, samsung phones but on IPAD isn't working. How can I make it work also on IPAD?</p>  <pre><code>if (document.documentElement.clientWidth &gt; 480 &amp;&amp; document.documentElement.clientWidth &lt; 1100) {           var getState = playerInstance.getState();         if(getState == 'playing' || getState != 'idle' || getState != 'buffering' || getState != 'paused' || getState != 'undefined'){             jwplayer().setFullscreen(true);          }else if (getState != 'playing' &amp;&amp; getState == 'paused'){             jwplayer().setFullscreen(false);          }     }else {         var getState = playerInstance.getState();         if(getState != 'playing' || getState == 'paused' || getState == 'idle' || getState == 'buffering'){             jwplayer().setFullscreen(false);          }          if(getState == 'undefined'){             jwplayer().setFullscreen(false);          }          if(getState == 'playing'){             jwplayer().setFullscreen(false);          }         if((navigator.userAgent.match(/iPhone/i))) {             jwplayer().setFullscreen(true);          }     } </code></pre>